hints.content: When we skip count by tens,  we add $10$ to each number as we count.

Nat started with $596$,  so we need to add $10$ more to $596$.

$596 + 10 = 606$

The next number Nat will say is $606$.

Nat is still skip counting by ten so we need to add $10$ to $606$.

$606 + 10 = 616$

The next number Nat will say is $616$.
